io.limberest.json

Interface Jsonable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonList, StatusResponse

    public interface Jsonable
    By convention Jsonables should have a constructor that takes a single argument of type JSONObject. To invoke default autobinding, the constructor can and should call bind(JSONObject).

    • Method Summary
